formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1.We have relied upon the estimates given by the management in case of costs other than construction
cost.
2.The preparation of the accompanying Statement is the responsibility of the Management of the Company. This responsibility
includes designing, implementing and maintaining internal control relevant to the preparation and presentation of the Statement,
and applying an appropriate basis of preparation; and making estimates that are reasonable in the circumstances.
3.The certificate is addressed to and provided to the promoters of the project solely for the purpose to enable comply with
requirement of RERA , and should not be used by any other person or for any other purpose. Accordingly, we do not accept or
assume any liability or any duty of care for any other purpose or to any other person to whom this certificate is shown or into
whose hands it may come without our prior consent in writing
4.The details mentioned in Annexure A such as carpet area, booking status, unit consideration, date of agreement to sale,
encumbrance status, name, KYC and mobile numbers of allottees are as provided by the management. Received amount has
been verified with the books of accounts.
5.The Inventory details attached to scanned certificate in annexure A are different than the figures uploaded in form 3A. We have taken a confirmation from the promoter as to identify the exact inventory vis-?-vis Form 3A and accordingly date of agreement for sale are updated in Form 3A.
6.The promoter has changed RERA account from Axis bank to ICICI Bank Limited. The application of change in RERA bank account at GujRERA is yet not done.
7.The promoter has accepted 100% of booking amount in RERA account and therefore amount withdrawn till date is taken as total amount accepted as booking.
8.The promoter has executed sale deed in favor of allottees and therefore IN form 3A we have mentioned date of sale deed in 3A.
